# Fretboard Navigation Playground
# Visualize moves on the neck

# Start in a familiar CAGED position
CAGED C 3   # C-shape at 3rd fret (Eb major chord)

# Move up the neck to the next inversion
move next_inversion

# Slide into a soloing position
slide from 3 5 to 5 7

# Define a specific position window
position 8 12
